⚡ Clean formulation

# Resource-Backed Monetary Layer
## Core Idea
Money can be backed by certified resources in place, not only extracted reserves.
## Layers
1. Resource Certification (measurement + audit)
2. Ownership & Registry
3. Monetary Claims (circulating layer)
4. Redemption / Extraction Mechanism
## Constraints
- confidence discount on in-place resources
- enforceable rights
- credible redemption pathways
## Principle
Backing = verifiable claim on future extractable value,
not just present physical stock.

⸻

🎯 Bottom line

You’re not literally “returning to the gold standard.”

You’re proposing:

A modernized, deferred-extraction backing system
where value is tied to verified reserves + future optionality

